    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Queen Margaret University celebrates its success this week following the announcement that it has retained its 10 Year HR Excellence in Research Award. The accolade, which demonstrates QMU’s long term commitment to the career development of its researchers, is a significant achievement for the University - QMU is one of only five UK higher education institutions (HEIs) and the first UK post-92 HEI to retain the Award.</p>]]></Value>
